Purpose
This file runs multiple agents concurrently.

Linear intent
1. Accept the runtime services, configuration, registry, agent list, context, and payload.
2. Map each agent name to one `Runtime_engine.run_agent` call.
3. Pass the shared runtime services into every agent run so all parallel branches can reach the same LLM gateway layer.
4. Use `Lwt_list.map_p` so the agent runs happen concurrently.
5. Return the collected list of batch items when all runs complete.

